📌 Smart Expense Tracker — Development Roadmap
🚀 Project Overview

A full-stack MERN application to track daily expenses with analytics, authentication, and smart insights. The project focuses on real-world usability, clean UI, and scalable architecture.

🧭 Phase 1: Frontend Foundation (Day 1–5)
🎯 Goal:

Build a fully functional UI with simulated backend (localStorage)

Tasks:
Setup React project
Configure folder structure
Build reusable components
Features:
User Authentication UI (Login/Register)
Dashboard layout
Add / Edit / Delete expenses (local state)
Expense list view
Category selection
Basic charts (monthly + category-wise)
Responsive design (mobile + desktop)
Tech:
React.js
Tailwind CSS
Recharts
⚙️ Phase 2: Backend Development (Day 5–8)
🎯 Goal:

Build secure and scalable backend APIs

Tasks:
Setup Node.js + Express server
Connect MongoDB
Create models and controllers
Features:
User authentication (JWT)
Password hashing (bcrypt)
Expense CRUD APIs
User-specific data handling
Middleware for protected routes
Tech:
Node.js
Express.js
MongoDB
JWT Auth
🔗 Phase 3: Integration (Day 8–10)
🎯 Goal:

Connect frontend with backend

Tasks:
Replace localStorage with API calls
Handle authentication tokens
Implement error handling
Features:
Secure login/logout
Real-time expense updates
API-based data fetching
Loading states & error UI
📊 Phase 4: Advanced Features (Day 10–12)
🎯 Goal:

Make the project stand out

Features:
Advanced analytics dashboard
Category-wise spending insights
Date filtering (weekly/monthly/yearly)
Export expenses to PDF
Dark / Light mode toggle
🚀 Phase 5: Deployment & Optimization (Day 12–14)
🎯 Goal:

Make the project production-ready

Tasks:
Deploy frontend (Vercel / Netlify)
Deploy backend (Render / Railway)
Environment variables setup
Optimize performance
Add-ons:
Clean UI polish
README documentation
Screenshots & demo link
🧠 Key Learning Outcomes
Full-stack application development (MERN)
Authentication & security (JWT)
REST API design
State management & UI structuring
Data visualization
Real-world problem solving
